        <i class="fa fa-play-circle play-button"></i>
      </div>
      <div class="section-inner">
        <h3>Our advocates made sure Hafsa's story was heard.</h3>
        <p>When Hafsa shared her powerful story of escaping human traffickers
        with our team, we knew it was one the world needed to hear. Thanks to
        our advocates who shared her story on Facebook, thousands were able to
        hear and were moved to respond.</p>
        <div class="highlights"><span class="bold">171</span> Shares &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="bold">5.8K</span> Views</div>
